Class IRCRawEventDispatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • event.IRCRawEventDispatcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRCRawEventListener

    public class IRCRawEventDispatcher
extends java.lang.Object
implements IRCRawEventListener
    This class is in charge of calling the command.onExecute() method for all the listeners, and then dispatch the corresponding IRCEvent with the eventDispatcher.
    Author:
    Tomas
